quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,71,Ndipo kumbukira tsiku limene tidzaitana mtundu uliwonse wa anthu pamodzi ndi Atsogoleri awo. Ndipo yemwe adzapatsidwa Buku lake ku dzanja lamanja iwo adzawerenga Bukulo mwa chisangalalo ndipo sadzaponderezedwa ngakhale ndi pang’onong’ono pomwe
  17,72,Koma iye amene ali wakhungu m’moyo uno adzakhalanso wakhungu m’moyo umene uli nkudza ndipo adzasochera kwambiri
  17,73,Ndithudi iwo adali pafupi kuti akusokoneze ku zimene takuvumbulutsira iwe kuti utinamizire zina ndipo zikadatero akadakupala ubwenzi
  17,74,"Ngati Ife tikadapanda kulimbikitsa chikhulupiriro chako, padatsala pang’ono kuti uwatsatire"
  17,75,Ndipo zikadatero Ife tikadakulawitsa chilango chachikulu m’moyo uno ndi chilango chachikulu m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Kotero siukadapeza wina aliyense wokuthandiza ku mkwiyo wathu
  17,76,"Ndithudi adatsala pang’ono kukuchititsa mantha m’dziko ndi cholinga choti akuchotse m’menemo. Zikadatheka kutero iwo sakadakhala pambuyo pako, koma kwa kanthawi kochepa"
  17,77,Umenewu ndiwo mwambo wa Atumwi amene tidatumiza iwe usanadze ndipo iwe siudzapeza kusintha kulikonse m’mwambo wathu